metadata.name: Just Pepe Dream
metadata.description: Broken dreams, dreams of wanting to have you around Dreaming of a car to buy and drive together. Dreamed of going to the beach, dreamed of being rich, dreamed of being comfortable, but the dream was destroyed by everything. with something to destroy it Make everything that is about to disappear. I'm heartbroken which everything is about to disappear As I reach my destination But at the end of the day there was nothing. because it's just a dream Besides the cat I love, Wrangle.
